jebbs.plantuml.prepublish: wget -O plantuml.zip https://sourceforge.net/projects/plantuml/files/1.2021.0/plantuml-jar-mit-1.2021.0.zip/download && unzip plantuml.zip && rm plantuml.zip && mv COPYING COPYING.plantuml-jar

ms-pyright.pyright.prepublish: npm i && cd packages/vscode-pyright && npm run prepackage

ms-python.python.prepublish: PIP_USER=no python3 -m pip --disable-pip-version-check install -r build/debugger-install-requirements.txt && python3 ./pythonFiles/install_debugpy.py && python3 -m pip install --no-deps --require-hashes --only-binary :all: -t ./pythonFiles/lib/python --implementation py -r ./requirements.txt && python3 -m pip install --no-deps --require-hashes --only-binary :all: -t ./pythonFiles/lib/jedilsp --implementation py --platform any --abi none -r ./pythonFiles/jedilsp_requirements/requirements.txt && python3 ./build/update_ext_version.py --release --for-publishing && npm run addExtensionPackDependencies && DISABLE_TRANSLATIONS=true npm run package

ms-toolsai.jupyter.prepublish: PIP_USER=no python3 -m pip --disable-pip-version-check install -t ./pythonFiles/lib/python --no-cache-dir --implementation py --no-deps --upgrade -r requirements.txt && npm run updateBuildNumber -- --buildNumber $GITHUB_RUN_ID && npm run package

ms-vscode.js-debug.prepublish: npm run compile && npm run package

custom: echo 'apt-get install -y apt-transport-https dirmngr gnupg ca-certificates' >> /tmp/build-godot.sh
echo 'su -c "npx --package vsce vsce package -o extension.vsix" node' >> /tmp/build-godot.sh
[ $MS_VERSION = '1.0.0' ] && npm remove --save-dev vscode && npm install --save-dev typescript@3 @types/vscode@1.23 @types/node@7 || true

vscode.smali.prepublish: cp LICENSE smali/ && cd smali && npm install

custom: [ $VERSION = '1.2.4' ] && npx haxelib install vscode && npx haxelib install vscode-debugadapter || true

wix.vscode-import-cost.prepublish: cd packages/vscode-import-cost && git clean -xdf && npm install
